group.name: Group_1
group.step:
##PARAM##
 a = 1
 b = 2
 #/PARAM##
 try:
 ##MAIN##
 	c = a + b
 #/MAIN##
 ##DONOTCHANGE##
 	result = 1
 	result_data = c
 except:
 	result = 0
 finally:
 	file = open("result","w")
 	file_data = open("result_data","w")
 	file.write(str(result))
 	file_data.write(str(result_data))
 	file.close()
 	file_data.close()
 #/DONOTCHANGE##
